      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and remains a reliable choice for daily transportation. While the engine and transmission perform their duties without issue, the exterior shows visible signs of age including several scratches, small dings, and some paint fading on the hood. The interior is clean but exhibits typical wear on the upholstery and floor mats. It has been regularly serviced and is ready for its next owner who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
